            <title><![CDATA[【九合一选举】国民党籍基隆市长候选人谢国樑自行宣布当选]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay">
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-11/3937702-ph.jpg?VersionId=dDCJj6m_1jQeU.Vel4l60kry2hejjvQm&amp;itok=AAzpZiUg" alt="" data-caption="国民党籍基隆市长候选人谢国樑（右）在票数超过9万票后，自行宣布当选基隆市长。（谢国樑脸书截取）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-11/3937702-ph.jpg?VersionId=dDCJj6m_1jQeU.Vel4l60kry2hejjvQm&amp;itok=AAzpZiUg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
      <figcaption><p>国民党籍基隆市长候选人谢国樑（右）在票数超过9万票后，自行宣布当选基隆市长。（谢国樑脸书截取）</p></figcaption>
  </div>
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-11/img_6871.jpg?VersionId=ctkXWTKZKHzQEQ52hHoVAUQSLXtXFssh&amp;itok=4M-fawHJ" alt="" data-caption="国民党籍基隆市长候选人谢国樑在票数超过9万票后，自行宣布当选基隆市长。" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-11/img_6871.jpg?VersionId=ctkXWTKZKHzQEQ52hHoVAUQSLXtXFssh&amp;itok=4M-fawHJ" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
      <figcaption><p>国民党籍基隆市长候选人谢国樑在票数超过9万票后，自行宣布当选基隆市长。</p></figcaption>
  </div>
  <div class="figure-media-gallery-nav"></div>
</div>     
            

<p>台湾在星期六（11月26日）举行九合一地方选举，国民党籍基隆市长候选人谢国樑在票数超过9万票后，自行宣布当选基隆市长。</p>
<p>据三立新闻报道，基隆市长选举中，国民党籍候选人谢国樑票数一路领先，在超过9万票后自行宣布当选。过去由民进党林右昌执政8年的基隆市如今蓝绿翻转。</p>
<p>谢国樑也在竞选总部前开直播，发表胜选感言。</p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
      


<div class="cx_paywall_placeholder" id="sph_cdp_40"></div>
       ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Sat, 26 Nov 2022 10:14:00 GMT</pubDate>
